Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.59,0:29:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心太
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.90,0:29:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太柔弱了 不适合剑客
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.57,0:29:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今开始 你就叫「剑心」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑… 心…










